FT  18 JUL 94 / China snubs UK minister
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By Our Beijing Correspondent
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
Prospects for a smooth transition by Hong Kong to Chinese control in 1997
dimmed at the weekend when the goodwill visit to Beijing of a UK Foreign
